-- Cornelius, Ricci Named Nomura's Co-Heads of Fixed-Income Sales for Europe
-- Gavin Finch
-- 2010-07-26T06:28:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-26/cornelius-ricci-named-nomura-s-co-heads-of-fixed-income-sales-for-europe.html

          
          
             Nomura Holdings Inc. named Guy
Cornelius and Raffaele Ricci co-heads of fixed-income sales for
Europe, the Middle East and Africa.  
 Cornelius joins from Evolution Securities Ltd., where he
was head of fixed income, Nomura said in an e-mail to employees
today. Ricci has worked at Nomura for the past two years and was
most recently head of solutions sales and co-head of sales for
southern Europe and the Middle East. Both will report to Georges
Assi and Kieran Higgins, Nomuraâ€™s co-heads of fixed-income for
Europe.  
 Patrick Meyer, a London-based spokesman for the bank,
confirmed the contents of the memo.  
